        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jeremy_holmes/{size}/1146_2.png",
        "created_at": "2018-11-08T21:39:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"147143\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I might join Jeremy\u2019s throng.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You leave my throng out of this.</p>\n<p>Well done Kent. Sounds excellent. I happened to have a Roulot '10 Meix Chavaux on the weekend. It was just ok, with some honey oxidative notes blunting the palate a little. Wish it was under screwcap.</p>",
